<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=UTF-8" />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=League+Spartan:wght@100..900&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    html, body {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
    }
    .email-body {
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 20px;
        max-width: 600px;
        min-height: 720px;
        background-color: #F3F4F6;
    }
    .container {
        width: 100%;
        min-height: 720px;
        background-color: white;
        border-radius: 8px;
    }
    .email-text {
        padding: 16px;
    }
    h3 {
        width: 100%;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 16px 0;
        text-align: center;
        font-family: 'League Spartan', 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
        font-size: 24px;
        font-weight: 600;
        color: #fff;
        background-color: #00B0BB;
        border-top-left-radius: 8px;
        border-top-right-radius: 8px;
    }
    p {
        display: block;
        margin-bottom: 16px;
        color: #111827;
        font-family: 'League Spartan', 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
        font-size: 14px;
        font-weight: 400;
        line-height: 1.5;
    }
    em {
        display: block;
        margin: 20px auto;
        padding: 16px;
        font-family: 'League Spartan', 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
        font-size: 20px;
        font-weight: 600;
        font-style: normal;
        letter-spacing: 1px;
        color: #00B0BB;
        text-align: center;
        background-color: #F3F4F6;
        border-radius: 8px;
        border: 2px solid #E5E7EB;
    }
    .info-box {
        margin: 24px 0;
        padding: 20px;
        background-color: #16A34A;
        border: 2px solid #15803D;
        border-left: 6px solid #166534;
        border-radius: 8px;
    }
    .info-box h4 {
        margin: 0 0 12px 0;
        color: #FFFFFF;
        font-family: 'League Spartan', 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
        font-size: 16px;
        font-weight: 600;
    }
    .info-box p {
        margin: 8px 0;
        color: #FFFFFF;
        font-size: 14px;
        line-height: 1.5;
    }
    .login-button-container {
        text-align: center;
        margin: 32px 0 24px 0;
    }
    .login-button {
        display: inline-block;
        padding: 16px 32px;
        background-color: #00B0BB;
        color: #ffffff !important;
        text-decoration: none;
        font-family: 'League Spartan', 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
        font-size: 16px;
        font-weight: 600;
        border-radius: 8px;
        border: none;
        cursor: pointer;
        transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
    }
    .login-button:hover {
        background-color: #00828bff;
    }
    .login-button:visited {
        color: #ffffff !important;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="email-body">
    <div class="container">
        <h3>E-mail Confirmado - Doutor Viu</h3>
        <div class="email-text">
          <p>Olá, <%= name %></p>
          <p>Seu e-mail foi confirmado com sucesso e sua conta no Doutor Viu está ativa.</p>
          <p>Data da confirmação:</p>
          <em><%= estimatedConfirmedAt %></em>
          
          <div class="info-box">
            <h4>✅ Conta Ativada</h4>
            <p>Agora você pode acessar todos os recursos da plataforma com segurança.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="login-button-container">
            <a href="<%= loginPageUrl %>" class="login-button">
              Acessar Doutor Viu
            </a>
          </div>
          
          <p>Bem-vindo ao Doutor Viu!</p>
          <p>Atenciosamente, Equipe Doutor Viu</p>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>